GAF Corp management lead chairman Samuel J. Heyman intend reconsider proposal acquire GAF. On September 8 offer 64.00 dlrs cash 2.50 dlrs principal amount 15 pct junior subordinate debenture due 2007 GAF share. Heyman own 2700000 GAF's 33.5 mln share outstanding. In letter committee independent director form consider offer Heyman modify term offer continue bid due rise rate financial market conditions. Heyman "In considerable elapse original proposal submit credit financial market experienced extraordinary unprecedented deterioration. As average rate financing propose raise connection acquisition increase original proposal approximately 150 basis points." He intend promptly review available option include revision offer reflect current market conditions. Reuter 